project_address: Near Chandranagar Bridge P.T. college road , Paldi
promoterAddress: 402, Center Plaza, Opp Sarthak School,  Ghatlodiya, Ahmedabad Ahmedabad 380054

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. On the basis of information given and records & documents provided to me, the partnership firm has borrowed monies from friends and relatives for development of project. The partnership firm does not have any outstanding loan from Banks or financial institutions for development of the above mentioned project.					
2. The audit for FY 2020-21 & FY 2021-22 as per Income Tax Act 1961 is pending while issuing this certificate. So the certificate is issued based on unaudited books of accounts. Further due to Audit Finalization for F.Y. 2019-20 there is change in books of accounts and result in reduction in some expenses.					
3. The firm has received Rs. 13,64,26,000 from members as booking advance and out of which Rs. 13,54,26,000 deposited into normal current account of the firm. The firm has not followed RERA regulations and guidelines in respect of booking advance. Such amount should be deposited into RERA account of the project. Further new booking made between 01.09.2022 to 31.10.2022 total amount received Rs. 23188000 not deposited into RERA retention account.
4. As per the information and explanation given and records & documents provided to me by the partners of the firm, the partnership firm has borrowed monies from various persons for development of the projects of the firm. Unsecured loans have not been borrowed for any specific project and it is a general loan for all the projects and hence it is not possible for me to bifurcate these borrowed amount to a specific project and hence the amount of loans shown here above are the total borrowings for all the projects of the partnership firm. The partnership firm does not have any outstanding loan from Banks or Financial Institutions for development of the above mentioned project.					
5. In some of the units where amount received is more than 10% of the unit value but no Agreement to sale has been made.
6. Interest cost on unsecured loans for F.Y. 2021-22 debited to P&L Account and re-invested in Unsecured loans account and not bifurcated to respective project cost as Audit is also pending and hence not considered in this form.
